            "answer_text": "He hadn\u2019t been diagnosed and wouldn\u2019t be until the following year. It\u2019s quite possible he had suspicions that he was hiv+ though. There are two things still to remember though. Firstly, that the song wasn\u2019t written by him, so although he gave a fantastic performance, his interpretation of the lyric isn\u2019t necessarily what Brian intended when he write it. And secondly, even if he didn\u2019t know he was ill, he still knew he was going to die, which is kind of the point of the song. ",
